title: The Tycoon 2FA Phishing Platform and the Collapse of Legacy MFA

content.raw: Tycoon 2FA enables turnkey real-time MFA relays behind 64,000+ attacks this year, proving legacy MFA collapses the moment a phishing kit targets it. Learn from Token Ring how biometric, phishing-proof FIDO2 hardware blocks these relay attacks before they succeed. [...]
